{"TopicId":165992,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Plugin questions","CreatedByName":"Jhorriga","CreatedById":180947,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-29T23:53:00Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Jhorriga","CreatedById":180947,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-29T23:53:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a plugin that allows parts to have their own landing gear (Home module landing gear) instead of having to place it on?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-30T03:07:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoving to Add-on Discussions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sebi.zzr","CreatedById":81294,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-30T17:08:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223183130\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022165992\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221506729180\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022180947\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jhorriga\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, Jhorriga said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a plugin that allows parts to have their own landing gear (Home module landing gear) instead of having to place it on?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou don\u0027t need any plugin for that.What you need is the right configuration.I suggest you to inspect the model in blender to see how the landing gear is \u0022rigged\u0022.Then you can use either stock module for landing gear\u00A0or \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/152782-130-kspwheel-physics-based-alternate-wheel-collider-api-only/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EKSPWheel\u003C/a\u003E.The easiest way to make landing gear working (deploy/retract) is to use \u003Ca href=\u0022https://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Module#ModuleAnimateGeneric\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EModuleAnimateGeneric\u003C/a\u003E,but there must not be any \u0022non supported transforms\u0022 in model.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jhorriga","CreatedById":180947,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-01T17:45:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlright. Would you be willing to volunteer with a project I\u0027m leading? Im trying to revive home and fixing the landing gear on the modules.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed2283999598\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/165986-home-revived/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:214px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}